[+++ b/README.md, +Highlighting attachments, +------------------------, +, +If you want to highlight your attachment content, you will need to store your file content and set `term_vector` as follow:, +, +```, +PUT test/my_type/_mapping, +{, +    "my_type" : {, +        "properties" : {, +            "my_html_file" : {, +                "type" : "attachment",, +                "fields" : {, +                    "title" : { "store" : "yes" },, +                    "my_html_file" : { "term_vector":"with_positions_offsets", "store":"yes" }, +                }, +            }, +        }, +    }, +}, +```]